---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Servicios — CONSTRU" description="Servicios de ingeniería y construcción industrial: galpones, obras civiles, edificación corporativa y remodelaciones. Calidad inquebrantable.">
  <!-- Hero Section for Services -->
  <section class="relative w-full h-[409px] md:h-[512px] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden border-b border-surface-container-high">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <div class="bg-cover bg-center w-full h-full opacity-30 grayscale"
        style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCbYRa-DhRl8NDLmR5nZDqrCMUBL-xMEyd7qH4B2S9o5_CPGLRGW3lYo7KPNyjqjbv_BrzqEV_gmbiKLMlvqsxwmsNPmZx-8HqlO7AApnn6GYelsGbUSD8bWepgW2MUquqauGBhjbWQw-d_iF7mfynQM2iZ2dYrBGQ45uida-VDgkaPfHE5tGbcsyLyV7gVWBvniNgl36mAQygKDl5gg9Pq1cagURJ1nLKZUbwvuLKzW1KABphHyI5f19FJDtfscf6dlRqz_-FWHQ')">
      </div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-background via-background/80 to-transparent"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-gutter max-w-container-max mx-auto">
      <h1 class="font-display-lg-mobile md:font-display-lg text-display-lg-mobile md:text-display-lg uppercase text-on-background mb-4 drop-shadow-lg">
        Nuestros Servicios
      </h1>
      <p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl mx-auto border-l-4 border-primary pl-4 text-left md:text-center md:border-l-0 md:border-t-4 md:pt-4 md:pl-0">
        Ingeniería de precisión y construcción robusta para el sector industrial. Desarrollamos proyectos
        integrales con estándares de calidad inquebrantables.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services Detailed Layout -->
  <section class="py-margin-mobile md:py-margin-desktop px-gutter max-w-container-max mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-16 md:gap-24">

      <!-- Service 1: Galpones y Naves Industriales -->
      <article class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center group">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5 order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary font-light" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 0;">factory</span>
            <span class="font-label-lg text-label-lg text-primary tracking-widest uppercase">Estructuras Metálicas</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-headline-xl text-headline-xl uppercase text-on-background mb-6">Galpones y Naves Industriales</h2>
          <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-6 text-justify">
            Diseño, fabricación y montaje de estructuras de acero de gran luz para uso industrial,
            logístico y comercial. Empleamos acero estructural de alta resistencia, optimizando el peso
            y garantizando la máxima durabilidad frente a cargas sísmicas y de viento.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 border-l border-surface-container-high pl-4">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm mt-1">check_circle</span>
              <span class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface">Diseño sismorresistente bajo normativa vigente.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm mt-1">check_circle</span>
              <span class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface">Fabricación automatizada en planta de alta precisión.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm mt-1">check_circle</span>
              <span class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface">Montaje rápido con control topográfico.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm mt-1">check_circle</span>
              <span class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface">Revestimientos térmicos y acústicos de alto desempeño.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border-2 border-on-surface text-on-surface font-label-lg text-label-lg uppercase px-6 py-2 hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-colors"
            href="/portafolio">
            Ver Proyectos <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 order-1 lg:order-2 relative h-[300px] md:h-[450px] w-full bg-surface-container overflow-hidden border border-surface-container-high group-hover:border-primary/50 transition-colors duration-500">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-surface-container-lowest to-transparent opacity-50 z-10"></div>
          <img class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale opacity-80 group-hover:grayscale-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-700"
            alt="Interior de galpón industrial con estructura metálica"
            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuB9nC7sDpHvGVP--_pnk-V_onbYwnofYysK9YwdXVf4nprs3P4HhaR00wZH2lbimqKPsiA0pdZXjWLjNw5LAfiNle941Du-KFD61NTa4ZAZ44zaqN0MSYeIQ9fuCNu60TlYbkFNHjKhhbH2suZmDCIBzHRrIf6Ox3fUuTnck9ewjZKfNvzmTCbTLUMuv8kNCsAjKinuHGZ6g4ejYY1NyhianfKn9Ns2uGkCg7ndIdxN3nBJWUPmNLJeNnSUr6keCeJvmy17UF-8OA" />
          <div class="absolute bottom-4 right-4 z-20 bg-background/90 px-4 py-2 border border-surface-container-high flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-surface-variant text-sm">straighten</span>
            <span class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-on-surface tracking-widest uppercase">Hasta 60m luz libre</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <hr class="border-surface-container-high" />

      <!-- Service 2: Obras Civiles y Movimiento de Tierra -->
      <article class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center group">
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 relative h-[300px] md:h-[450px] w-full bg-surface-container overflow-hidden border border-surface-container-high group-hover:border-primary/50 transition-colors duration-500">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-bl from-surface-container-lowest to-transparent opacity-50 z-10"></div>
          <img class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale opacity-80 group-hover:grayscale-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-700"
            alt="Maquinaria pesada en excavación de terreno"
            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCTCx__UTVTDXOLu8aXnX4eRiXWAon8Sm9ggkExVhvwp5xR_VJRgPTImD9zDv9Ag4iTi_Kw0fZgXUj6u_Q2VH6o7v_5qHNAIVOgExkFZJfzBqJ0P9B0Hf96LEt3uF32Qmal6jhUQtWmbpuz-wRfyELCqweOWel0Z8BAKJj6N6GJVSEE3PHyO7Tn4F5CmMiS5aFgaUO631XkmWacg0anxHoAdz9C50j1J2H5m5f4x72Npd5bow6yvIS4CFWpy8wsUIjLCQmRiNwuEA" />
          <div class="absolute top-4 left-4 z-20 bg-background/90 px-4 py-2 border border-surface-container-high flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-surface-variant text-sm">terrain</span>
            <span class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-on-surface tracking-widest uppercase">Estabilización</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary font-light" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 0;">foundation</span>
            <span class="font-label-lg text-label-lg text-primary tracking-widest uppercase">Fundaciones</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-headline-xl text-headline-xl uppercase text-on-background mb-6">Obras Civiles y Movimiento de Tierra</h2>
          <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-6 text-justify">
            Ejecución integral de fundaciones, losas, muros de contención y preparación del terreno.
            Aseguramos la base de su proyecto mediante estudios geotécnicos rigurosos y ejecución
            mecánica de alta capacidad para garantizar la estabilidad estructural a largo plazo.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 border-l border-surface-container-high pl-4">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm mt-1">check_circle</span>
              <span class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface">Excavaciones masivas y perfilado de terreno.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm mt-1">check_circle</span>
              <span class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface">Fundaciones superficiales y profundas (pilotes).</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm mt-1">check_circle</span>
              <span class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface">Losas industriales de alto tráfico (radieres).</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm mt-1">check_circle</span>
              <span class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface">Redes sanitarias y canalizaciones subterráneas.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border-2 border-on-surface text-on-surface font-label-lg text-label-lg uppercase px-6 py-2 hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-colors"
            href="/portafolio">
            Ver Especificaciones <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <hr class="border-surface-container-high" />

      <!-- Service 3: Edificación Corporativa -->
      <article class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center group">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5 order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary font-light" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 0;">corporate_fare</span>
            <span class="font-label-lg text-label-lg text-primary tracking-widest uppercase">Arquitectura Funcional</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-headline-xl text-headline-xl uppercase text-on-background mb-6">Edificación Corporativa</h2>
          <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-6 text-justify">
            Construcción de edificios de oficinas, centros de operaciones e instalaciones
            administrativas vinculadas a complejos industriales. Integramos diseño arquitectónico
            moderno con funcionalidad operativa, priorizando la eficiencia energética y el confort
            ambiental.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 border-l border-surface-container-high pl-4">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm mt-1">check_circle</span>
              <span class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface">Estructuras mixtas (acero-hormigón).</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm mt-1">check_circle</span>
              <span class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface">Fachadas vidriadas y envolventes térmicas.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm mt-1">check_circle</span>
              <span class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface">Instalaciones clima (HVAC) y corrientes débiles.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm mt-1">check_circle</span>
              <span class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface">Terminaciones de alto estándar y durabilidad.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border-2 border-on-surface text-on-surface font-label-lg text-label-lg uppercase px-6 py-2 hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-colors"
            href="/portafolio">
            Ver Portafolio <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 order-1 lg:order-2 relative h-[300px] md:h-[450px] w-full bg-surface-container overflow-hidden border border-surface-container-high group-hover:border-primary/50 transition-colors duration-500">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-surface-container-lowest to-transparent opacity-50 z-10"></div>
          <img class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale opacity-80 group-hover:grayscale-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-700"
            alt="Edificio corporativo moderno con fachada vidriada"
            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCziUQK7-6cMwzdeHAbBZBj-lmg52ndkhNNjDpMdhXIizW1ImZt8pAChVysv3-wjqjYrYk_dcrjAAEZm820ILXpQOawFyEg4hymhI7liIwq7xOOS-xJ_j-CM7ch4465pePwAklTU3W1dU1o5f7xC71EgEU1n1IwHoIWnU0FEoZbnW9mQjarhMSHTKO8tohM_GLHhslm-AOXmGcoRfRAzelaUduPfWDbF8UnTO0Y9MzDbrCdYnci3AB1kUteskjaRkhmE19GSEYcXg" />
          <div class="absolute bottom-4 right-4 z-20 bg-background/90 px-4 py-2 border border-surface-container-high flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-surface-variant text-sm">energy_savings_leaf</span>
            <span class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-on-surface tracking-widest uppercase">Eficiencia Energética</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <hr class="border-surface-container-high" />

      <!-- Service 4: Remodelaciones y Ampliaciones -->
      <article class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center group">
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 relative h-[300px] md:h-[450px] w-full bg-surface-container overflow-hidden border border-surface-container-high group-hover:border-primary/50 transition-colors duration-500">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tl from-surface-container-lowest to-transparent opacity-50 z-10"></div>
          <img class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale opacity-80 group-hover:grayscale-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-700"
            alt="Interior industrial en proceso de remodelación estructural"
            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCG_KrbXZoanQVrs6Jwl-Km5r8etqkLFxiAi4089p7moj9UAOeQZDNMgjt9drbJYuvX_qhggwB0v1DTOhlZpgJt76A_nblFHl3KbZgKYQ6G6fqQmdRA5klblYAGet8xj_y3EePfusQf1ic0VZC1NBW0RRl3KhxsVy4qyyZ82dYRQwDU7qQsJJtFWtjF-4XNxoum8Li5r0xiY34kdHBo10wpUhel3zf2ketFgE9LRjKUS4RtIgJ731kcPH-g4yDVnnLAaaj8ua_8bg" />
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 z-20 bg-background/90 px-4 py-2 border border-surface-container-high flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-surface-variant text-sm">construction</span>
            <span class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-on-surface tracking-widest uppercase">Upgrade Estructural</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary font-light" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 0;">architecture</span>
            <span class="font-label-lg text-label-lg text-primary tracking-widest uppercase">Adaptación</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-headline-xl text-headline-xl uppercase text-on-background mb-6">Remodelaciones y Ampliaciones</h2>
          <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-6 text-justify">
            Actualización y expansión de instalaciones industriales existentes. Evaluamos la capacidad
            estructural actual e intervenimos con soluciones que minimizan la disrupción operativa,
            permitiendo el crecimiento de su planta o centro de distribución.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 border-l border-surface-container-high pl-4">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm mt-1">check_circle</span>
              <span class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface">Refuerzo estructural de elementos existentes.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm mt-1">check_circle</span>
              <span class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface">Altillos estructurales para maximización de volumen.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm mt-1">check_circle</span>
              <span class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface">Cambio de cubiertas y revestimientos.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm mt-1">check_circle</span>
              <span class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface">Planificación por fases para operación continua.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border-2 border-on-surface text-on-surface font-label-lg text-label-lg uppercase px-6 py-2 hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-colors"
            href="/portafolio">
            Casos de Estudio <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </article>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="bg-surface-container-low border-t border-b border-surface-container-high py-16 px-gutter text-center">
    <h2 class="font-headline-xl text-headline-xl uppercase text-on-background mb-4">¿Proyecto en Mente?</h2>
    <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant max-w-xl mx-auto mb-8">
      Nuestro equipo de ingeniería está listo para evaluar sus requerimientos y estructurar una solución
      constructiva óptima.
    </p>
    <a class="inline-block bg-primary-container text-on-primary-container font-label-lg text-label-lg uppercase tracking-widest px-8 py-4 font-bold hover:bg-primary transition-colors"
      href="/contacto">
      Contactar Asesor
    </a>
  </section>
</Layout>
